title: The Weekend Bite - Week Ending February 18th, 2022
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: This week on The Weekend Bite, Jerry Kronenberg, Director of News at Seeking Alpha, discusses notable 13F filings from well known Hedge Funds, Jay Pestrichelli from ZEGA Financial talks the microenvironment with us, and Uma Pattarkine, CFA from CenterSquare Asset Management shares her outlook on Real Estate and ESG investing in the space.
